Information on Majors
Unsure of which major you may want? Want to know more about that major? Click below to find which majors each college at UIC has, and to find information on those majors in two ways.
We encourage you to visit your college's information for students on degree programs in addition to the information provided at the Academic Major Report in the state of Illinois.




